milestones.description: Wasim Raja has broken the record for most ducks (6) in ODIs for PAK, going past Sarfraz Nawaz's 5
Tahir Naqqash and Ramiz Raja's 64-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 57 between Sarfraz Nawaz and Zaheer Abbas
